```plantuml
@startuml chirgjin_track-my-events

actor User
participant "React Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Gateway Service" as Gateway
participant "User Service" as UserService
participant "Tracking Service" as TrackingService
participant "Redis Pub/Sub" as Redis
participant "PostgreSQL" as DB

User -> Frontend: Accesses Dashboard
Frontend -> Gateway: GET /dashboard (with auth token)
Gateway -> UserService: Validate token
UserService --> Gateway: Token validation response
Gateway -> TrackingService: GET /events/overview
TrackingService -> DB: Query event statistics
DB --> TrackingService: Return statistics
TrackingService --> Gateway: Return dashboard data
Gateway --> Frontend: Return dashboard data
Frontend --> User: Display dashboard

User -> Frontend: Triggers event (via SDK)
Frontend -> Gateway: POST /events (with SDK key)
Gateway -> TrackingService: Validate SDK key
TrackingService --> Gateway: Key validation response
Gateway -> Redis: Publish event to "events" channel
Redis -> TrackingService: Event notification (async)
TrackingService -> DB: Store event data
DB --> TrackingService: Storage confirmation

User -> Frontend: Registers new account
Frontend -> Gateway: POST /users/register
Gateway -> UserService: Forward registration
UserService -> DB: Create user record
DB --> UserService: User creation confirmation
UserService --> Gateway: Registration response
Gateway --> Frontend: Registration response
Frontend --> User: Show success message

User -> Frontend: Logs in
Frontend -> Gateway: POST /auth/login
Gateway -> UserService: Forward login
UserService -> DB: Verify credentials
DB --> UserService: Credential verification
UserService --> Gateway: Return auth tokens
Gateway --> Frontend: Return auth tokens
Frontend --> User: Store tokens and redirect

@enduml
```